"You snooze, you lose"?

518
01:01:51,905 --> 01:01:56,144
- It's an expression.
- That's beautiful.

519
01:01:56,686 --> 01:01:59,154
That's bullshit!

520
01:02:00,290 --> 01:02:01,814
This is bullshit, man!

521
01:02:01,814 --> 01:02:06,657
Don't deal with these people! They
sold us out. They will sell you out, too.

522
01:02:52,609 --> 01:02:54,406
want to help me in the garden?

523
01:02:56,846 --> 01:02:57,596
OK.

524
01:03:07,490 --> 01:03:11,119
Our tomatoes are looking good,
