599
01:11:20,082 --> 01:11:21,845
And today I saw Gage.

600
01:11:29,892 --> 01:11:33,919
Thank you for your trust, David.
And for listening.

601
01:11:34,564 --> 01:11:36,498
- Did you fuck him?
- No!

602
01:11:36,498 --> 01:11:40,659
