The man was a fucking stallion.

610
01:12:05,826 --> 01:12:08,829
Is that what you want me to say?
We did it all night.

611
01:12:08,829 --> 01:12:11,798
- Is that the truth?
- You don't want the truth.

612
01:12:11,798 --> 01:12:16,701
