639
01:15:23,392 --> 01:15:27,590
I will take it.
I mean, if nobody else wants it.

640
01:15:50,186 --> 01:15:52,814
- Hi.
- Hi, Diana.

641
01:16:06,936 --> 01:16:10,963
<i>The next few weeks without David</i>
<i>felt like months.</i>

642
01:16:10,963 --> 01:16:14,098
<i>I got very good at staring at walls.</i>

643
01:16:14,098 --> 01:16:18,077
Diana, Diana.

644
01:16:18,077 --> 01:16:19,704
