723
01:24:50,892 --> 01:24:54,419
I didn't know whether
you like big ones or little ones.

724
01:24:56,865 --> 01:25:00,357
You're so beautiful. Come here.

725
01:25:03,005 --> 01:25:06,839
I didn't have much time
